      "description": "A hulking orderly frozen mid-stride; his eyes follow you, but he never moves."
    }
  ],
  "items": [
    {
      "id": "master-key",
      "name": "Master Key",
      "description": "A large, tarnished key hanging behind the reception desk. It feels heavy and cold.",
      "foundIn": "foyer",
